source.name: 2008 Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Annual Report
source.description: This file contains the Social Security Administration's 2008 FOIA Annual Report.  The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2008.  It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
